postcontent:
This PP Super is in excellent condition. All of its original accessories, serial numbered box, owners manual and holster are included.
The PP Super is an all-steel, blowback double action pistol. It features an external slide stop lever and a manual decocker on the left side of the slide. There is no manual safety, however there is a firing pin safety. It is intended to be carried with the chamber loaded ready to be fired in double action mode. The magazine catch is located on the side grip next to the trigger guard.
Caution: The 9x18mm Police/Ultra ammunition is NOT compatible with the Soviet 9x18 Makarov PM ammunition. Attempting to fire the 9x18 Makarov ammunition from a PP Super is EXTREMELY dangerous due to the larger diameter of the 9mm Makarov bullet.
